Text: The WTI Bullet swap contractsFollowing the email you have received yesterday concerning the new WTI bullet swap contracts we would like to summarize what we have done on the ICE system yesterday evening Deleted WTI monthly time spreads Deleted WTIBrent monthly diff spreads spread with legging Deleted NYH Harbor Fuel Oil Crack monthly spread with legging Added WTIBrent monthly diff spreads spread with NO legging Added NYH Harbor Fuel Oil Crack monthly spread with NO legging Unfortunately the WTIBrent and the NYH Fuel Oil Crack contracts with the legging functionality have been removed from your portfolios You will need to add the first four nearby months contracts to your portfolios by going to Admin Manage Portfolios Edit your portfolio Please do not hesitate to contact us is you have any question Helpdesk on US Stephanie Trabia UK Regards Stephanie Trabia Marketing Manager IntercontinentalExchange Tel Fax Mob

ICE Order Size Cc ATTENTION PHYSICAL NATURAL GAS TRADERS In response to user requests ICE has lowered the minimum incremental order size from mmbtus to mmbtus for all physical natural gas orders only This change will become effective June If you have any further questions please call one of the following for assistance Joe Adevai Pam Anderson Bud Hum
